*Jaramillo, J. and Moraes, L. (2000), &quot;Dualily and reflexivity in spaces of polynomials&quot;, &quot;Arch. Math. (Basel)&quot; 74: 282–293. 
*Mujica, Jorge (2001), &quot;Reflexive spaces of homogeneous polynomials&quot;, &quot;Bull. Polish Acad. Sci. Math.&quot; 49:3, 211–222. </text><links>
